chord.analyses.typestate
Class TypeStateParser

java.lang.Object
  chord.analyses.typestate.TypeStateParser

public class TypeStateParser
extends java.lang.Object

Parser for type-state spec. Start state can be anything the user specifies. There is a designated implicitly defined error state named "Error". Grammar of spec file: Updates -- ... Asserts ---... ... Example: test.LockClass UnLocked Updates Lock-UnLocked-Locked UnLock-Locked-UnLocked Asserts Lock-UnLocked UnLock-Locked

Author:
machiry
